<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Access Code</title>
</head>

<body
  style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 20px;">
        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding-bottom: 20px;">
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
                style="background-color: #000; width: 100%; text-align: center;">
                <tr>
                  <td
                    style="color: #fff; padding: 10px; margin: 0; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-weight: bold; font-size: 24px;">
                    ://AuthN</td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <h2 style="color: #000; font-size: 20px;">New Device Access Code</h2>
              <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
              <p>We've detected a login attempt from a new device. To ensure the security of your account, please use
                the following access code to verify your identity:
              </p>
              <p
                style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: #f0f0f0; border: 1px solid #ccc;">
                {{link}}
              </p>
              <p>Enter this code on the verification page to complete the login process. If you did not attempt to log
                in from a new device, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
              <p>This access code will expire in 15 minutes for security reasons.</p>
              <p>Best regards,<br><span
                  style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-weight: bold;">://AuthN</span></p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin-top: 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
        <p>This email was sent to {{email}}. If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>

</html>